@page "/"

<div class="dashboard-container">
    <div class="welcome-card">
        <h1 class="app-title">Pschool Management System</h1>
        <p class="app-subtitle">A streamlined solution for managing parents and students efficiently.</p>

        <div class="divider"></div>

        <section class="overview-section">
            <h3>Project Overview</h3>
            <p>
                Pschool is a lightweight school management system developed using
                <strong>ASP.NET Core Web API</strong> for backend services and
                <strong>Blazor WebAssembly</strong> for the frontend.
            </p>
            <p>
                The system enables administrators to easily manage student and parent information,
                maintain relationships between them, and ensure smooth data handling with an intuitive interface.
            </p>
        </section>

        <section class="features-section">
            <h3>Core Features</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>View, create, and update parent and student records</li>
                <li>Associate students with respective parents</li>
                <li>Search and filter records dynamically</li>
                <li>Clean, responsive, and user-friendly design</li>
                <li>Backed by Entity Framework Core and SQL Server</li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="navigation-section">
            <h3>Get Started</h3>
            <p>Use the sidebar to navigate:</p>
            <ul>
                <li><b>Parents</b> — Manage parent profiles and details</li>
                <li><b>Students</b> — Manage student information and assignments</li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <footer class="footer">
            <p>© @DateTime.Now.Year Pschool Management System. All rights reserved.</p>
        </footer>
    </div>
</div>